snippet.title: 🚨 Announcement Teaser: Vermeer Pack
snippet.description:
Vermeer, inventor of the round baler as you know it, is soon joining Farming Simulator 22. The upcoming Vermeer Pack, included in the Year 1 Season Pass, will be available on August 23rd.

🤓 More info on the blog!
► https://farming-simulator.com/newsArticle.php?&news_id=372

🛒 Get Farming Simulator 22 now on the official shop!
► https://farming-simulator.com/buy-now.php

👨‍🌾 Learn how to play with the Farming Simulator Academy!
► https://farming-simulator.com/academy
